      • getStationsFromString

        public java.util.HashMap<Node,Edge> getStationsFromString(java.lang.String str)
        Returns a Map of Nodes with labels containing the string specifed. If an exact match isn't found it'll try use half the string to partially map it to a result.
        Parameters:
        str - as String this is the Station name we would like to find
        Returns:
        a Map of Stations and their edges. (Incase multiple stations share the same name, we want to be able to identify them)
